    "shortDescription": "<p>You fire a shimmering arrow of pure order from your holy symbol at any one target in range as a ranged touch attack.</p><p>A chaotic creature struck by an <i>arrow of law</i> takes 1d8 points of damage per two caster levels (maximum 5d8). A chaotic outsider instead takes 1d6 points of damage per caster level (maximum 10d6) and is dazed for 1 round. A successful Will save reduces the damage to half and negates the daze effect.</p><p>This spell deals only half damage to creatures that are neither chaotic nor lawful, and they are not dazed. The arrow has no effect on lawful creatures.</p>",
